Subject: Job Error post Netwrix Enterprise Auditor (NEA) 11.6.0.80 patching
Solution_Comment__c:
Patched the current version of Stealth application(s) running in the Environment:
FROM:
Netwrix Enterprise Auditor (NEA)    11.6.0.80 
NEA Access Information Center       11.6.0.16
NEA Proxy                                         11.6.0.26

TO:
Netwrix Enterprise Auditor (NEA)    11.6.0.82
NEA Access Information Center       11.6.0.21

To correct the Access Violation noted in the Bug fix documentation, post NEA patching we had to run the FS_UpdateProxy job to push the updated files 
https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Install/FileSystemProxy/Upgrade.htm
